import React from 'react';
import {Container,
    Content,Card
     ,CardImg,Title,
     Kategoriya,Price,
     OtherName,Deleted,
     Edited}  from './style'

     import apple from '../../../assets/imgs/apple.png'
const Mahsulotlar1 = () => {
  return(
      <Container>
             <Content>

                  <Card>
                       <CardImg  src={apple}/>
                       <Title>Lavash mini</Title>
                       <Kategoriya>Lavash</Kategoriya>
                       <Price>18,000 UZS</Price>
                       <OtherName>Kichkina lavash, bla bla</OtherName>
                       <Deleted>deleted</Deleted>
                       <Edited>edited</Edited>
                  </Card>

                  <Card>
                  <CardImg  src={apple}/>
                  <Title>Lavash mini</Title>
                  <Kategoriya>Lavash</Kategoriya>
                  <Price>18,000 UZS</Price>
                  <OtherName>Kichkina lavash, bla bla</OtherName>
                  <Deleted>deleted</Deleted>
                  <Edited>edited</Edited>
             </Card>

             </Content>
      </Container>
  )
};

export default Mahsulotlar1;
